<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a2Mar1927"><font color="red">2 March 1927</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I had to revise <font face="wake">w</font> and read it again for the editors of <i>Transition</i>. They liked it so much that they want the suite for the April number and will then reprint May to July the <i>Criterion</i>, <i>This Quarter</i>, and <i>Navire</i> so as to publish seriatim all Part I. </div>
